-- U.S. Auto Sales Will Top 17 Million in 2015, IHS Automotive Says
-- B y   K e i t h   N a u g h t o n
-- 2010-12-02T18:38:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-02/u-s-auto-sales-will-exceed-17-million-in-2015-ihs-automotive-forecasts.html
U.S. automobile sales will exceed 16
million in 2014 and 17 million in 2015, Michael Robinet,
director of global production forecasts for researcher IHS
Automotive, said today in a presentation to the Automotive Press
Association in Detroit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Naughton in Detroit at 
